<plot>In director Nick Alexanders comedy, brothers Jackson (Daniel Taylor, "My Name Is Earl") and Lucas (Jeremy Dozier), a couple of reclusive online investors, have lived lives without leaving the safety of their home, until the day fugitive Lola (Lauren Evans, "Lipstick Jungle") knocks on their door saying she is being chased by her boyfriend Joey (Brian Newell, "Law and Order: Special Victims Unit"). With FBI Agent Solondz (John Prudhont, "Castle" and "Kath and Kim") in pursuit, will the recluses end up with the girl, in jail or dead?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?564228</url></doc>
